members.name: attachedNotes
members.doc:
Notes created and attached to the account upon successful site block.
If accountId of the given user == siteOwnerId then 1 note will be attached to this account.
Otherwise 2 notes will be attached: 1 for the account of the user and another one for the site owner.
If empty then adding a note failed.
